    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! Thanks for stopping by to check out my pride and joy. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to see her go, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed with love. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape, looking and driving just like it did the day I brought it home. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly cherished and is ready for the open road, you\u2019ve found it. Come by, say hi, and let\u2019s see if she\u2019s the right fit for you!",
